# Quality gates

Every feature slice must explicitly cover:
- permissions
- state transitions
- exception handling and recovery
- analytics events
- acceptance criteria

Enterprise architecture gates for v1.6 (apply when relevant):
- spatial correctness (`GEOGRAPHY`, `ST_MakeValid`, area variance guard)
- lineage performance (O(1) runtime traversal; materialized lineage fields)
- offline conflict integrity (HLC ordering, idempotency behavior)
- TRACES NT resilience (payload size/vertex chunking and reference reconciliation)
- GDPR compliance safety (cryptographic shredding without breaking retention obligations)

Then update:
- feature doc
- quality docs (if changed)
- status logs
